"use strict";(self.webpackChunkgatsby_starter_default=self.webpackChunkgatsby_starter_default||[]).push([[665],{7163:function(e,t,a){a.r(t);var n=a(6540),s=a(6998),i=a(2484);t.default=()=>n.createElement(s.A,null,n.createElement(i.A,{title:"AI Principles"}),n.createElement("div",{className:"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12"},n.createElement("h1",{className:"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6"},"JobMinglr’s AI Principles"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8"},"In 2024, JobMinglr publicly committed to fairness in its use of algorithms. With rapid developments in AI since then, we are excited to share our principles for the ethical and beneficial use of AI at JobMinglr. Our approach is guided by an open mind and a desire to learn and improve, with the ultimate goal of helping our users find meaningful employment."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Job Seeker First"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"JobMinglr’s mission is to help people find jobs. We strive to open access to opportunities for all job seekers. The development, management, and use of AI are guided by this mission and principle above all others."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Center Fairness and Equity"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"Talent is universal, but opportunity is not. Without proper care, the biases and barriers job seekers face can be reinforced or amplified by AI. Appropriate controls and oversight, including compliance with JobMinglr’s privacy policy, are essential for the success of AI systems and the protection of job seekers. We are committed to fairness and equity in our products, ensuring that AI benefits job seekers and building a diverse and representative team."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Addressing Hiring Inequalities"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"Globally, individuals encounter barriers and unfair biases in the hiring process. As a leading job platform, we aim to leverage our technology, expertise, and reach to eliminate these biases and ensure everyone has access to quality employment. We are dedicated to helping 30 million job seekers facing bias and barriers secure jobs by 2030."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Listen and Learn"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"A commitment to fairness and equity requires nuance, expertise, and dedication. These concepts are highly contextual and vary across cultures. There is no single definition of fairness or equity. We use both quantitative and qualitative data to rigorously evaluate our products’ fairness from initial design onward, incorporating the lived experiences of job seekers. We understand that learning is a journey and that this work is never finished."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Hiring is Human"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"AI offers opportunities to augment, assist, and support people in their work. However, hiring is fundamentally a human process, and humans will always play vital roles in job seeking and hiring. Decisions about jobs and hiring are among the most important in people’s lives, and we aim to preserve the human element while improving and simplifying the experience of finding the right job or candidate."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Innovate Responsibly"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"The rapid development of AI has opened many exciting new opportunities for job seekers and employers. However, responsible innovation requires care, consideration, and clear-eyed assessment. Our systems must be accountable for their outcomes, transparent in their impact, and well-governed with robust security and safety measures. They must respect human rights and carefully consider the risks and potential benefits. We welcome open dialogue about the uses of AI in job seeking, advertising, and hiring."),n.createElement("h2",{className:"text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4"},"Responsible AI at JobMinglr"),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"JobMinglr’s cross-functional Responsible AI team builds tools, systems, and processes that advance responsible and inclusive technology. Team members contribute to the development of machine learning and AI systems, from responsible design to ongoing model monitoring."),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6"},"We advocate for industry-wide action and embed best practices across the HR tech industry, starting with tools for teams at JobMinglr. We have participated in workshops with industry leaders to discuss best practices and ethical technology and engaged with policymakers on legislative and regulatory proposals around AI, including the National Institute of Standards and Technology’s AI Risk Management Framework."),n.createElement("p",{className:"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"},"We continue to monitor global best practices to help job seekers everywhere gain equal access to opportunities.")))}}]);
